                <mxCell id="tenancy_note" value="Multi-Tenancy Model: every request resolves tenant_id from the JWT/API key, propagated as a connection-scoped PostgreSQL session variable (app.current_tenant_id), enforced by Row-Level Security on every table. Qdrant collections are additionally namespaced per knowledge_base_id which is itself tenant-scoped at creation time. Cross-tenant data access is architecturally prevented, not just access-controlled." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff3e0;strokeColor=#e65100;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;align=left;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
